Task: write the **bundle** index for aho iteration {{ iteration }}.

A bundle is the single document a future agent or engineer reads to recover the full context of this iteration. It must:
- Identify the iteration, project, and date.
- List the canonical artifacts (design, plan, build-log, report, run-report) with their paths and a one-line summary of each.
- Capture the most important decisions and any open follow-ups for the next iteration.
- Be at least 250 words and reference workstream ids.

Output the markdown document only.
